Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}提著稍有些汙漬的行李包
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}什麼也不知道 從天空降落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:42.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}從地圖的正對面 在這裡登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}在這夢中憧憬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:48.37,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yea Yea Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:51.36,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The Rock City Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:54.34,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yea Yea Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:57.39,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The Rock City Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:01.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh baby 跳吧 跳吧 跳越牆壁 With my guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:04.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}直到傳達到為止 oh yeah 唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:06.95,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just music 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:09.73,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}奉獻給你喔 oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:13.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}真的有很多相同點嗎? With my guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:16.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}邊探索 Yea 邊唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:19.11,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just love 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:21.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}追趕上 be free!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:25.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}My 完美夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:40.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}睡時也好醒時也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:43.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}把夢作為同伴哦 Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:44.82,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wanna believe the singing on beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:46.51,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}most recently is like recess for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:47.76,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}pretty pretty please,no birds and the bees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:49.50,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}but ecstasy with extra cheese
